That's all right.

01:03:36.730 --> 01:03:38.397
What are you doing?

01:03:38.482 --> 01:03:40.316
Oh, just tinkering.

01:03:40.400 --> 01:03:41.567
Oh.

01:03:42.444 --> 01:03:46.197
