to peek.

01:04:05.217 --> 01:04:07.384
I'm not peeking,
I'm looking.

01:04:07.469 --> 01:04:09.136
Do you think
they like each other?

01:04:09.221 --> 01:04:10.638
Of course they do.

01:04:10.722 --> 01:04:12.264
