pirates around here,
are there, Truly?

01:04:32.035 --> 01:04:34.703
Oh, I'm sure there are.
Hundreds of them.

01:04:34.955 --> 01:04:36.038
'Course there are.

01:04:36.122 --> 01:04:38.457
