Well, let me see.

01:04:47.926 --> 01:04:50.219
A boat!
I can see a boat!

01:04:51.805 --> 01:04:53.222
A boat?

01:04:54.766 --> 01:04:58.435
Did you say, "a boat"?
That isn't just any
old boat out there.

01:04:58.520 --> 01:04:59.562
No?
No?

01:04:59.646 --> 01:05:04.900
