notorious Baron Bomburst.

01:05:04.985 --> 01:05:06.443
Baron Bomburst?
Baron Bomburst?

01:05:06.528 --> 01:05:10.698
You have never heard
of Baron Bomburst,
ruler of Vulgaria?

01:05:10.782 --> 01:05:13.242
The most evil man
in the world!

01:05:13.326 --> 01:05:14.785
