MAN: (EXCLAIMS) Yes!

01:05:40.895 --> 01:05:43.439
That car!

01:05:43.523 --> 01:05:44.607
MAN: Yeah, yeah, yeah,
yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:05:44.691 --> 01:05:46.775
