me an argument?

01:05:49.154 --> 01:05:50.946
No, Your Excellency.
Stand by the boats!

01:05:51.031 --> 01:05:52.948
Stand by the boats!
Man the grappling hooks.

01:05:53.033 --> 01:05:54.825
Man the grappling hooks.
And load the cannon!

01:05:54.909 --> 01:05:56.660
Load the cannon!
(CLAMORING)

01:05:56.995 --> 01:05:58.287
He's awful.

01:05:58.371 --> 01:05:59.455
He's terrible.

