that's easier said
than done.

01:06:12.886 --> 01:06:14.386
But why, Daddy? Why?

01:06:14.471 --> 01:06:15.804
Well, I'll tell you.

01:06:16.222 --> 01:06:20.017
What none of us have noticed
is while we've
been sitting here,

01:06:20.101 --> 01:06:23.479
