my two spies?

01:10:19.257 --> 01:10:21.884
Ah, there you are.

01:10:22.510 --> 01:10:27.264
Now, then, I have
a secret mission for you.

01:10:27.557 --> 01:10:29.099
You will go ashore,

01:10:29.183 --> 01:10:32.352
