01:13:48.674 --> 01:13:54.012
I thought I'd grown
immune to them

01:13:55.139 --> 01:13:58.350
And yet

01:13:59.852 --> 01:14:04.147
He's such a love

01:14:05.525 --> 01:14:11.905
He's such a lovely,
lonely man

01:14:12.532 --> 01:14:16.535
