01:19:22.883 --> 01:19:24.426
What have you. . .
Ah, ah!

01:19:27.805 --> 01:19:30.056
I have an idea.

01:19:39.567 --> 01:19:43.361
Now, remember,
we are supposed to be
English gentlemen.

01:19:43.863 --> 01:19:46.197
