Wouldn't be offering you
a contract unless they did.

02:21:10.420 --> 02:21:11.671
Sign here, please.

02:21:13.423 --> 02:21:15.466
Wait. Don't go away.
I'll be right back.

02:21:15.551 --> 02:21:16.884
